    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 5000i and 9000i - CAB ACCESSORIES - OPERATION - INTERVISION
        DISPLAY
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>INTERVISION DISPLAY</title>
        <para>The Intervision display receives battery power from the (B1) battery adapter through 5A fuse F10-A.
            Switched ignition power is supplied from the (I2) ignition adapter through 5A fuse F10-B. Ground for the
            display unit is supplied from the (G1) ground adapter. The unit connects to the truck data link on circuits
            98G(+) and 98H(-).
        </para>
    </svcproc>
